oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Concert for Asia at the Belcourt Theatre
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Folds, Ben, 1966-; Keaggy, Phil; Mosser, Jonell; Ryan, Matthew; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color lobby card (green and teal on white) announcing Concert for Asia featuring Ben Folds, Marcus Hummon, Phil Keaggy, Lisa McClendon, David Mead, Jonell Mosser, Anna Owens, Matthew Ryan, Annie Sellick, Annette Strean, and Jason White at the Belcourt Theatre on February 14. Poster features a woodcut of a sun.
